---
---
<section class="pt-14 lg:pt-16 lg:min-h-screen flex flex-col lg:flex-row border-b border-secondary-100">
  <!-- Left Column: Text Content -->
    <div class="w-full lg:w-1/2 flex flex-col justify-center px-8 md:px-16 lg:px-24 py-16 lg:py-20 bg-white">
    <div class="max-w-xl space-y-8">
      <!-- Title -->
      <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-6xl xl:text-7xl font-extrabold leading-[1.05] text-text-main">
        Tu catálogo online en minutos. <br/>
        <span class="text-primary-500">Simple para arrancar, potente para escalar.</span>
      </h1>

      <!-- Description -->
      <p class="text-lg text-text-muted font-normal leading-relaxed max-w-2xl">
        Cargá tus productos, compartilos por WhatsApp y empezá a recibir pedidos hoy. Sin código, sin comisiones, sin depender de nadie.
      </p>

      <!-- CTA Buttons -->
      <div class="flex flex-col gap-4 pt-4">
        <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4">
          <a
            href="https://admin.purocatalogo.com/register"
            class="btn-primary h-12 px-8 rounded-full"
            onclick="window.trackEvent && window.trackEvent('cta_click', {cta_location: 'hero', cta_text: 'Creá tu catálogo gratis'})"
          >
            Creá tu catálogo gratis
          </a>

        </div>
        <p class="text-[11px] text-text-muted font-medium flex items-center gap-4">
          <span class="flex items-center gap-1"><span class="material-symbols-outlined text-sm text-primary-500" aria-hidden="true">check_circle</span> Sin tarjeta de crédito</span>
          <span class="flex items-center gap-1"><span class="material-symbols-outlined text-sm text-primary-500" aria-hidden="true">bolt</span> Listo en 2 minutos</span>
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- Right Column: Live Catalog Demo -->
  <div class="w-full lg:w-1/2 bg-background-subtle flex items-center justify-center p-6 md:p-8 lg:p-12 relative overflow-hidden border-t lg:border-t-0 lg:border-l border-secondary-100">

    <!-- Phone Frame with Live Catalog -->
    <div class="relative w-full max-w-[340px] lg:max-w-[380px] mx-auto">
      <!-- "Live" indicator -->
      <div class="flex items-center justify-center gap-2 mb-4">
        <span class="relative flex h-2 w-2">
          <span class="animate-ping absolute inline-flex h-full w-full rounded-full bg-green-400 opacity-75"></span>
          <span class="relative inline-flex rounded-full h-2 w-2 bg-green-500"></span>
        </span>
        <span class="text-[10px] font-bold text-secondary-400 uppercase tracking-widest">Catálogo en vivo</span>
      </div>

      <!-- Phone Shell -->
      <div class="relative aspect-[9/18] bg-secondary-900 rounded-[2.5rem] p-3 shadow-2xl border border-secondary-800">
        <!-- Notch -->
        <div class="absolute top-0 left-1/2 -translate-x-1/2 w-28 h-6 bg-secondary-900 rounded-b-2xl z-20"></div>

        <!-- iframe container -->
        <div class="w-full h-full rounded-[2rem] overflow-hidden bg-white relative">
          <!-- Skeleton placeholder while loading -->
          <div class="absolute inset-0 z-10 bg-white flex flex-col items-center justify-center gap-3 transition-opacity duration-500" id="hero-iframe-skeleton">
            <div class="w-10 h-10 border-2 border-primary-200 border-t-primary-500 rounded-full animate-spin"></div>
            <span class="text-xs text-secondary-400 font-medium">Cargando catálogo...</span>
          </div>

          <iframe
            src="https://maklab.com.ar/"
            title="Ejemplo de catálogo creado con PuroCatálogo - Mak-Lab"
            class="w-full h-full border-0"
            loading="lazy"
            sandbox="allow-scripts allow-same-origin allow-popups"
            onload="document.getElementById('hero-iframe-skeleton').style.opacity='0'; setTimeout(() => document.getElementById('hero-iframe-skeleton').style.display='none', 500);"
          ></iframe>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Prompt to interact + link -->
      <div class="flex items-center justify-center gap-3 mt-4">
        <p class="text-[11px] text-secondary-400 font-medium flex items-center gap-1.5">
          <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-sm" aria-hidden="true">touch_app</span>
          Navegá el catálogo — es real
        </p>
        <span class="text-secondary-200">|</span>
        <a
          href="https://maklab.com.ar/"
          target="_blank"
          rel="noopener noreferrer"
          class="text-[11px] font-bold text-primary-500 flex items-center gap-1 hover:gap-1.5 transition-all"
        >
          Abrir sitio <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-sm" aria-hidden="true">open_in_new</span>
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

